descriptionHtml:
So this is my ENB + FXAA setting for Skyrim. I slightly edited ENB HD6 Lighting Enhancement preset and created FXAA profile to tweak it a little. See it for yourself.

INSTALLATION:
1. Install FXAA Injector.
2. Extract all files from ENB-FXAA folder to your Skyrim root.
3. Start with Skyrim Launcher to reconfigure.

NOTIFICATIONS:
Be sure to check Ultra Settings.
SSAO enabled. Be ready for FPS drops.

CREDITS to Boris Vorontsov, HeliosDoubleSix and some_dude.

Sorry for my English ;)

P.S. Night screenshots looking a bit dark. But in game nights are not so dark. I believe it is converter fault.
author: kruzz85
